################
README for bang.
###############

Bang is a collection of script that generates images ranges for use
with libthc widgets collection.

Requirements :

- Perl
- Image Magick
- perlmagick

Use :

    ./fader.pl size_x size_y



Notes :

More options will be added in future version of this package.
the style of the images will be greatly improved.
potar.pl for rotary is coming soon.y
